Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Who shot our queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Look for the shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave no stone unturned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Tai! Queen Otohime! I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do with this anger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! We found the shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Get to the rooftop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the shooter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a gun in his hand. There is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe-san! We just killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It will ruin the Queen's efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to rest in peace like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because he was a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if he was a pirate or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Hody! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...who killed our queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Queen Otohime was killed by a human!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't deserve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...killed the Queen who wanted nothing but peaceful coexistence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and broke our hearts just when we were inspired by her words and about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...extend our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He took our beloved one's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even by taking your life, Otohime-sama can never come back, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no justice in this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sad! Unbelievably sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the King still in Hard Shell Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of the Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear that? He's lost all control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.82,0:07:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open it while I have this urge to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,King-sama, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of the Left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The shooter had a gun in his hand so one of our soldiers shot him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.83,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have killed him even if he were unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.50,0:08:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Otohime would not allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when this cycle of revenge started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I kill somebody, I would only perpetuate that cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing my actions would make children's eyes cold
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and they would harbor hatred and become bitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the cycle of revenge spiraling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I could relate to what Otohime was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...as long as it was somebody else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.84,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...why shouldn't I kill the man who shot my wife to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand that-jamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As a soldier, I have taken many lives in reprisal for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed many humans who besieged us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I thought I have no place helping Otohime in what she was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so I just stood by and watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should an innocent one like her die and a man like me still live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take over her quest because my hands are sullied
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,by what I have done in the past-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But we all change and we all are full of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We Fishmen, and humans too. And there are things that only soldiers can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.71,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,520)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)\t(2490,2535,\1a&HFF&)}A few days later
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.71,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,520)\4a&HFF&}A few days later
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my own wife's funeral - I have to attend it-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Father-sama! Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to make you feel so left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Father-sama, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.95,"Sign",,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}"To Shirahoshi"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These letters keep flying in wherever I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There are already 5 of them, Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...a love letter! But Shirahoshi is only 6 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:30.01,"Sign",,0,0,0,,"I'm in luv with you. I suspect. Marry me.\NVander Decken"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is Vander Decken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.01,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the name of a pirate family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My children won't attend the funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be an accomplice still lurking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And catch this pirate named Decken now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Prince Fukaboshi! --Prince-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukaboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Citizens of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I want to tell you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So please give me your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In her last moment, my mother said happily,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"We are almost there at that place under the real sun."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We have decided to take over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,our mother's dream and dedicate our lives to seeing it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Princes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably are not going to be ready for the World Summit in 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But there will be another one in 6 years and another in 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this tragedy made you change your view of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will get rid of all the signatures that were left unburned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And when your emotional wounds heal someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,let's dream about the sun together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And for the decade that followed, not just Fukaboshi, Ryuboshi and Manboshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but also the King and the Princess spoke to the nation through the monitor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all while signatures kept mounting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was how we have been fighting against discrimination for the last 16 years
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the beginning of the Fishman Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong, who did horrible things to your hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,was like a brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If he engaged in violence, we were willing to go anywhere in order to stop him ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but he always paid off the Navy soldiers around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...to keep his actions secret from the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, I made you and many others suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you cut your own belly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay her with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:16:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I still won't forgive you but it could relieve Nami-san of her pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nami-san, what they have done to you was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a different story! This man didn't mean to hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take any punishment! If it makes you happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop. The only one I hate is Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm glad that you are not the mastermind of the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.65,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're Luffy's friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I've gone through hell because of the Arlong Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I met my friends in that horrible turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing led to another and I am who I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna hate you because you're a Fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't pity me because of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not so bad because I'm enjoying it in the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So it doesn't matter who did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell the people on the island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.13,0:17:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither the tragedy we endured nor of our anger towards humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You two grew up together and he's like a brother to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you couldn't just kill him even though you were justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve such words of kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Jinbe-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I know how hard it is to be a big brother! You're the man, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Tiger and Otoshime and everybody very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've been feeling so much pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! I thought it was unusual for you to listen so quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Jinbe, are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? I am not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! I said I am not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... Oh, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And Jinbe, what did happen to the thief that Wimpy's mother caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've been sleeping most of the time! That was the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Was it? --It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so your name is Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nami-chin, she's the Princess! You can't say "Hey"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was crying remembering my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She was quite a woman, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are Nami-chin-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:20:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Mermaid Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-chin is like her nickname. Her real name has no "chin."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like I have known you since I was a kid although we just met for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel comfortable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.70,0:20:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? Maybe that's because we've been through similar things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I took too much time. I need to know who is still at the Ryugu Palace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody and his crew invaded the palace and captured the King and his soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.39,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't know what happened to four of your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all the information we have so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If things are going as Hody planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole country might be in a terrible state by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what his plan is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspected he was up to something in the Fishman District
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,after retiring from the army,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but he never revealed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody hates humans more than Arlong-san did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been living on the resentment and anger of the Fishmen, and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is something about him clearly different from Arlong-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlong-san would look down on humans but he would never hurt other Fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hody will attack those Fishmen who are sympathetic to humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This year is the World Summit which takes place every four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.53,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they gathered enough signatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,King Neptune will express his intention to the world finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to relocate Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he is planning to block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he wants more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Video Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's projecting something on the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.95,0:22:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That's him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:22:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, everybody on Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the captain of the New Fishman Pirates from the Fishman District,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody broadcasts his ambition across all of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His shocking intention is to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and establish himself as the new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.83,0:23:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The citizens of Fishman Island had been deeply unsettled already,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but Hody's announcement has further filled them with dread!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.37,0:23:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Kingdom in Shock\NOrders to Execute Neptune"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
